text: Ic Lufa mid Godes gefeancilla Deiwes soecende & smeagende ymb mine saulðearfe mid Ceolnoðes ærcebiscopes geðeahte & ðara hiona et Cristes cirican.

Willa ic gesellan of ðem ærfe ðe me God forgef & mine friond to gefultemedan<../images/etail.gif>lce gereLXambra maltes &CLhlafa,Lhwitehlafa,CXXelmeshlafes, an hriðer, an suin,IIIIweðras,IIw<../images/etail.gif>ge spices & ceses, ðem higum to Cristes circcan for mine saule & minra frionda & mega ðe me to gode gefultemedan & ð<../images/etail.gif>t sie simle to adsumsio Sanctæ Marie ymbXIImonað.
End sue eihwelc mon swe ðis lond hebbe minra ærbenumena ðis agefe & mittan fulne huniges,Xgoes,XXhenfuglas.
Ic Ceolnoð mid Godes gefe ercebiscop mid Cristes rodetacne ðis festnie & write.
Ic Luba eaðmod Godes ðiwen ðas forecwedenan god & ðas elmessan gesette & gefestnie ob minem erfelande et Mundlingham ðem hiium to Cristes cirican.
& ic bidde, & an Godes libgendes naman bebiade ðæm men ðe ðis land & ðis erbe hebbe et Mundlingham, ðet he ðas god forð leste oð wiaralde ende.
Se man se ðis healdan wille & lestan ðet ic beboden hebbe an ðisem gewrite, se him seald & gehealden sia hiabenlice bledsung.
Se his ferwerne oððe hit agele, se him seald & gehealden helle wite, bute he to fulre bote gecerran wille Gode & mannum.
